<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SimpliScapes | Free Landscaping Quote</title>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      background: #0b3d2e;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px 40px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
    }

    .hero {
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501004318641-b39e6451bec6') center/cover no-repeat;
      height: 90vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    .overlay {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 700px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 42px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .hero p {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .form-box {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 30px auto 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .form-box input, .form-box select {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      background: #16a34a;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      font-size: 16px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .benefits {
      padding: 60px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #f9fafb;
    }

    .benefits h3 {
      font-size: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .benefit-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .benefit {
      padding: 20px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .testimonials {
      padding: 60px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .testimonial {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .cta {
      background: #16a34a;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    footer {
      background: #0b3d2e;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>SimpliScapes</h1>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="overlay"></div>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <h2>Get Your Dream Outdoor Space</h2>
    <p>Request your FREE landscaping consultation and transform your property today.</p>

    <div class="form-box">
      <h3>Request a Free Quote</h3>

      <form>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" required>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" required>
        <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number" required>

        <select required>
          <option value="">Select Service</option>
          <option>Front Yard Landscaping</option>
          <option>Backyard Landscaping</option>
          <option>Patio Installation</option>
          <option>Garden Design</option>
        </select>

        <button class="btn">Get My Free Quote</button>
      </form>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="benefits">
  <h3>Why Choose SimpliScapes?</h3>

  <div class="benefit-grid">
    <div class="benefit">
      <h4>Professional Design</h4>
      <p>Custom landscape designs tailored to your home and lifestyle.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefit">
      <h4>Full-Service Installation</h4>
      <p>From concept to completion, we handle everything.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefit">
      <h4>Free Consultations</h4>
      <p>Start your project with a no-obligation quote.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="testimonials">
  <h3>What Our Clients Say</h3>

  <div class="testimonial">
    "Professional, quick, and on budget. We love the final result!"
  </div>

  <div class="testimonial">
    "Amazing design and execution. Highly recommend!"
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <h3>Ready to Transform Your Yard?</h3>
  <p>Book your free consultation today and bring your vision to life.</p>
  <button class="btn">Start My Project</button>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 SimpliScapes | London, Ontario</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
